  "frontCover": "Front cover of a birthday greeting card, in a charming cartoon watercolor style. The scene depicts two stylized characters and a fluffy dog. On the left, a character with glasses, dark messy hair, and a wide-eyed, panicked expression is running and wielding a large paintbrush, splattering vibrant blue and orange paint across the upper left of the card. On the right, a character with dark hair pulled into a bun, a serene smile, and eyes closed, is holding a small paintbrush and gently petting a black and white fluffy dog. A three-tiered birthday cake with pastel yellow and pink icing, decorated with delicate patterns, sits to the right of the text. The text \"Happy Birthday, Gejhs!\" is prominently displayed in the center in a warm, brown, handwritten cursive font. The background features soft watercolor washes in shades of beige, light yellow, and subtle hints of blue and pink, with visible paper texture and organic paint bleeds. The overall mood is humorous and energetic, with a cohesive color palette and artistic execution.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a birthday greeting card, in a complementary watercolor style to the front. The design is a simple yet creative artistic flourish. A large, stylized paintbrush, tipped with a small blob of vibrant red paint, is depicted vertically on the left side of the card. Below the brush, a few soft watercolor splotches in yellow, blue, and pink are scattered, echoing the paint splatters from the front cover. The main decorative elements are focused towards the center and left, with a serene, muted color palette of soft yellows, creams, and subtle pastel hues. The right side and bottom-right corner are intentionally left mostly clear, with a small decorative flourish of watercolor wash in the bottom left to frame the composition. The overall impression is one of quiet artistic resolution and a subtle continuation of the theme without any text or characters."
